com.googlecode.aluminumproject.libraries

Interface Library

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurationElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLibrary

    public interface Library
extends ConfigurationElement
    A library.

    A library consists of a set of actions, action contributions, and functions. Libraries may support dynamic actions (the names of which are not known until runtime); whether or not this is the case can be found by inspecting their library information.
